  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "chapterTitle": "第7章 自由",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300064234_12_2375-2433",
          "range": "2375-2433",
          "rangeStart": 2375,
          "rangeEnd": 2433,
          "markText": "最令我介怀的一点是，我喜欢这份工作，也想努力做好它，但是做一份自己喜欢却无法掌控时间的事和做自己讨厌的事没什么区别。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1774832216,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-30 08:56:56",
          "chapterUid": 12,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300064234&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=2375&rangeEnd=2433",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ab326d0813ab7f97g014662?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=2375&rangeEnd=2433"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300064234_12_2562-2671",
          "range": "2562-2671",
          "rangeStart": 2562,
          "rangeEnd": 2671,
          "markText": "人们喜欢一切尽在自己掌握的感觉，就好像坐在生活的驾驶席上。当他们被要求做一些事时，他们会觉得自己没有话语权，没有选择权，选择是别人替他们做出的。所以，他们会拒绝做这件事或故意去做其他事，即使他们本来可能很乐意做这件事。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1774832115,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-30 08:55:15",
          "chapterUid": 12,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300064234&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=2562&rangeEnd=2671",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ab326d0813ab7f97g014662?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=2562&rangeEnd=2671"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300064234_12_1170-1223",
          "range": "1170-1223",
          "rangeStart": 1170,
          "rangeEnd": 1223,
          "markText": "与我们考虑过的任何客观生活条件相比，对自己的生活拥有强烈的掌控感是预测幸福这种积极感受的一项更可靠的指标。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1774832102,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-30 08:55:02",
          "chapterUid": 12,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300064234&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1170&rangeEnd=1223",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ab326d0813ab7f97g014662?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1170&rangeEnd=1223"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "chapterTitle": "第1章 没有人真的对钱失去理智",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
